rom\": 1309, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"any limitations\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not say,because I have only run this time, I will not make it,because you can,\\\" recalls the 31-year-old.\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And do not expect things from others, because they could have a world record and might go out in the first heat.\\\"\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"a world record\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"the first heat\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the long distance runner, it's all about leaving any self-doubt in the changing rooms so she can give it her all on the track.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the long distance runner\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"any self-doubt\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"the changing rooms\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1704}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Muir views bad races and knock-backs as opportunities to grow even stronger.\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Muir\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"bad races\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"knock-backs\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Make sure you learn from your experiences,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your experiences\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ask yourself what went wrong and how you can make it better?\\\"\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Molly Caudery World indoor pole vault champion Molly Caudery is one of GB's brightest stars - and she says staying positive has helped her achieve her childhood dream of representing her country.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1995, \"end\": 2008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\", \"score\": 0.999995872758395, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Molly Caudery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\"}, {\"begin\": 2019, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9594241304126565, \"rank\": 0.04141527346373865, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Molly Caudery World indoor pole vault champion\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"her childhood dream\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"her country\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Allowing self-doubt to creep in during pole vault could have detrimental outcomes, so she approaches every run-up with confidence, which allows her to fly over the bar gracefully.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"self-doubt\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"pole vault\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"detrimental outcomes\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"every run-up\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2258}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Cornish athlete, 24, also tries to keep a positive outlook, regardless of the result.\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2329, \"end\": 2336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cornish_people\", \"score\": 0.972804959655445, \"rank\": 0.027947962435067437, \"text\": \"Cornish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cornish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cornish_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a positive outlook\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every setback I have been presented with, I try and put a positive spin on it.\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a positive spin\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I learn from it, so it is not a negative anymore,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every time I am competing, whether it has gone good or bad, I always have fun and enjoy the moment,\\\" Caudery adds.\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"Caudery\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Pole vault is a lot easier than it looks, you just have to have a bit of courage to give it a go.\\\"\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pole vault\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2744}, {\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"a go\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Callum Wilkinson Northamptonshire race walker Callum Wilkinson has overcome career-threatening injuries in the lead up to the Paris Olympics, and believes that in order to achieve greatness, you need to be your own biggest fan - especially as race walking is arguably the most \\\"misunderstood sport\\\" in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2775, \"end\": 2791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Wilkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Callum Wilkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Wilkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Wilkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2793, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silverstone_Circuit\", \"score\": 0.9964938610639267, \"rank\": 0.003516970435584556, \"text\": \"Northamptonshire\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silverstone_Circuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silverstone_Circuit\"}, {\"begin\": 2822, \"end\": 2838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Wilkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Callum Wilkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Wilkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Wilkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"career-threatening injuries\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2943}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"your own biggest fan\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"the most \\\"misunderstood sport\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3072}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It suits my character, as an underdog who is going to fight for something against the odds,\\\" says the 27-year-old.\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my character\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"an underdog\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"the odds\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have got to be your own biggest fan.\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your own biggest fan\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When there is no one else cheering for you, you have got to back yourself.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Confidence for me is always evidence-based,\\\" he adds.\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Confidence\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the most confident that I have been in the last three years, because I had my best result in three years.\\\"\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last three years\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3447}, {\"ngram\": \"my best result\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3477}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having a tight-knit circle of positive people around him has also helped.\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tight-knit circle\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3522}, {\"ngram\": \"positive people\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The belief in my inner circle has always been that I could compete with the very best,\\\" says Wilkinson.\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The belief\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3582}, {\"ngram\": \"my inner circle\", \"from\": 3586, \"to\": 3601}, {\"ngram\": \"Wilkinson\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Surround yourself with good people, who support you do and understand what it takes.\\\"\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good people\", \"from\": 3700, \"to\": 3711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morgan Lake Paris will be Morgan Lake's third Olympics, and the high jumper has experienced ups and downs with her confidence along the way.\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3764, \"end\": 3775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Lake\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Morgan Lake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Lake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Lake\"}, {\"begin\": 3777, \"end\": 3782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999885781109, \"rank\": 1.1421791740645893e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3791, \"end\": 3802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Lake\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Morgan Lake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Lake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Lake\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the high jumper\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3839}, {\"ngram\": \"ups\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3859}, {\"ngram\": \"downs\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3869}, {\"ngram\": \"her confidence\", \"from\": 3875, \"to\": 3889}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She began her athletics career in heptathlon, so it took some time for her to build confidence in high jump.\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 4014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her athletics career\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3936}, {\"ngram\": \"heptathlon\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 3963, \"to\": 3972}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 4000}, {\"ngram\": \"high jump\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never thought in my wildest dreams that I would be an Olympic high jumper,\\\" says the 27-year-old.\", \"from\": 4016, \"to\": 4116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my wildest dreams\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4053}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic high jumper\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Once I dropped heptathlon and was just a high jumper, I did feel imposter syndrome for quite a few years.\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a high jumper\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4170}, {\"ngram\": \"imposter syndrome\", \"from\": 4183, \"to\": 4200}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a few years\", \"from\": 4205, \"to\": 4222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought, this is not really my event - this is not where I am meant to be.\\\"\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my event\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, staying true to her goals helped her overcome these feelings.\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her goals\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4337}, {\"ngram\": \"these feelings\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's also learned not to compare herself, having experienced the intense pressure that came with starting her Olympic career at Rio while still a teenager.\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4503, \"end\": 4506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999985892646638, \"rank\": 1.410737371233659e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the intense pressure\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4456}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic career\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of expectation that I would just rise and rise super quickly, but I struggled to get the best out of myself for years,\\\" says Lake.\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4548}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4563}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4666}, {\"ngram\": \"Lake\", \"from\": 4674, \"to\": 4678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes when I am jumping these heights, I think, 'Argh, I was jumping these 11 years ago'.\", \"from\": 4680, \"to\": 4774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these heights\", \"from\": 4709, \"to\": 4722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But, when I look back about how my younger self did those things, I had no limits and no comparison, I was just jumping really freely.\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my younger self\", \"from\": 4809, \"to\": 4824}, {\"ngram\": \"those things\", \"from\": 4829, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"no limits\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4858}, {\"ngram\": \"no comparison\", \"from\": 4863, \"to\": 4876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I try not compare myself to my previous self or to other people.\\\"\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my previous self\", \"from\": 4944, \"to\": 4960}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 4967, \"to\": 4979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Georgia Bell Last year, 30-year-old Georgia Bell was unranked, unsponsored and working in tech sales - and now she is heading to Paris to represent her country in the 1,500m.\", \"from\": 4983, \"to\": 5158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4983, \"end\": 4990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\", \"score\": 0.7460410292001693, \"rank\": 0.30377487960180505, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\"}, {\"begin\": 5020, \"end\": 5027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\", \"score\": 0.7460410292001693, \"rank\": 0.30377487960180505, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\"}, {\"begin\": 5113, \"end\": 5118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999885781109, \"rank\": 1.1421791740645893e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tech sales\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5083}, {\"ngram\": \"her country\", \"from\": 5131, \"to\": 5142}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,500m.\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being an accomplished runner in her teens, she quit after facing a series of injuries while at university.\", \"from\": 5160, \"to\": 5274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an accomplished runner\", \"from\": 5174, \"to\": 5196}, {\"ngram\": \"her teens\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5209}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 5233, \"to\": 5241}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 5245, \"to\": 5253}, {\"ngram\": \"university\", \"from\": 5263, \"to\": 5273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But taking up parkruns a few year ago reignited the passion - and self-belief is one of her tools.\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parkruns\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5297}, {\"ngram\": \"the passion\", \"from\": 5323, \"to\": 5334}, {\"ngram\": \"self-belief\", \"from\": 5341, \"to\": 5352}, {\"ngram\": \"her tools\", \"from\": 5363, \"to\": 5372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone is so physically good, but I think the real differences are made with people who can handle the pressure and go in and not let the self-doubt creep in,\\\" Bell says.\", \"from\": 5375, \"to\": 5548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5384}, {\"ngram\": \"the real differences\", \"from\": 5420, \"to\": 5440}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5455, \"to\": 5461}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 5477, \"to\": 5489}, {\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 5538, \"to\": 5542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really confident and can put that mental side together well, which is why I am beating people who, on paper, should be beating me.\\\"\", \"from\": 5549, \"to\": 5686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that mental side\", \"from\": 5584, \"to\": 5600}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5642, \"to\": 5648}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 5657, \"to\": 5662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Listening to upbeat music before a race also helps Bell get in the right mindset: \\\"I race my best when I am in a good mood and relaxed, so I like listening to a bit of Dua Lipa, especially Illusion.\\\"\", \"from\": 5688, \"to\": 5887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5856, \"end\": 5864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dua_Lipa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.430628375835066e-38, \"text\": \"Dua Lipa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dua_Lipa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dua_Lipa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 5708, \"to\": 5713}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 5721, \"to\": 5727}, {\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 5739, \"to\": 5743}, {\"ngram\": \"the right mindset\", \"from\": 5751, \"to\": 5768}, {\"ngram\": \"a good mood\", \"from\": 5799, \"to\": 5810}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 5847, \"to\": 5852}, {\"ngram\": \"especially Illusion\", \"from\": 5866, \"to\": 5885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also emphasises the importance of bouncing back after a confidence knock-back.\", \"from\": 5889, \"to\": 5971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 5909, \"to\": 5923}, {\"ngram\": \"a confidence knock-back\", \"from\": 5947, \"to\": 5970}]}, {\"sentence\":